<div class="well center">
	<h1>BiF Grammar - The Fassler Color Method</h1>
	<%= image_tag("color_wheel.png", :alt => "BiF Grammar Color Wheel") %>
	<h3>Do you struggle with English Grammar?</h3>
	<p>
		BiFluent uses a unique approach to teaching English grammar.
		<br>
		Try out our free demo below and learn more about the Fassler Color Method.
